@startuml
title Use Case: Generate Report

actor "Officer" as O
actor "Supervisor" as S
actor "Records System" as RS

usecase "Generate Report" as UC

O --> UC : creates report
S --> UC : reviews/approves
RS --> UC : stores/filing

UC .> (Enter Details) : include
UC .> (Add Evidence) : include
UC .> (Submit for Review) : include

UC <.. (Statistical Report) : extend <<if aggregate data>>
UC <.. (Public Version) : extend <<if public release>>
UC <.. (Court Package) : extend <<if legal proceedings>>

note right of UC
  Creates official documentation
  Multiple report types
  Supervisor approval required
  Legal and statistical uses
end note
@enduml
